snippet.title: King of the Cul-de-sac Release Trailer
snippet.description:
When her older brother leaves for college, Karah becomes the new toughest kid in the neighborhood! Giant spider moms. ancient forest gods, and alien warlords can't stop her from getting the crown, and becoming the new King of the Cul-De-Sac!

Depending on the choices made during Karah's journey, her final confrontation could be against anyone in the neighborhood. Don't fear failure -- no matter what you decide, every ending is a good ending!

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1064030

PC/Android/Mac/Linux on itch.io:
https://vimislikart.itch.io/kingoftheculdesac

Play directly in your browser on itch.io:
https://vimislikart.itch.io/kingoftheculdesac-web

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kotculdesac.beta&hl=en_US

Amazon Kindle:
Coming Soon!

Music is "Hate Me" from Green Dreams:
https://greendreams.bandcamp.com/

To keep up to date on updates and future projects, please follow me on twitter @vimislikart
